    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive excellence, this vehicle remains in absolute showroom condition. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero imperfections, protected by a professional ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin feels as if it just left the factory; the premium leather remains supple with no visible wear, and every electronic component functions flawlessly. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, having been meticulously maintained exclusively by certified specialists with a full paper trail included. Garage-kept under a soft cover and never driven in inclement weather, this car represents the pinnacle of its class. Included are both original keys, all factory manuals, and a clean title. For the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection, this is the one.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
